name: Dispatchable Capacity
description: Capacity of committed units between technical limits

name: Capacity Factor
description: Proportion of installed or rated capacity generating

name: Pump Load
description: Load drawn by a unit in pumping mode

name: VO&M Cost
description: Total variable operation and maintenance cost

name: Fixed Costs
description: Total fixed costs including amortized build costs

name: Net Profit
description: Net profit = net revenue - fixed costs

name: Max Capacity
description: Maximum generating capacity of each unit

name: Capacity Built
description: Capacity built (Max Capacity x Units Built)

name: Capacity Retired
description: Capacity retired (Max Capacity x Units Retired)

name: Hours Charging
description: Number of hours in charging state

name: Hours Discharging
description: Number of hours in discharging state

name: Hours Idle
description: Number of hours in idle state

name: VO&M Cost
description: Total variable operation and maintenance cost

name: Units Built
description: Number of BESS units built in this year

name: Build Cost
description: Cost of building a BESS unit

name: Units Retired
description: Number of BESS units retired in this year

name: Pump Load
description: Load drawn by exporting generators running in pumping mode

name: Unserved Energy Hours
description: Number of hours of unserved energy (USE)

name: Dump Energy Hours
description: Number of hours of dump energy

name: Hours Generation Curtailed
description: Number of hours that non-positive-priced generation has been curtailed

name: Total System Cost
description: Total system cost including fuel, VO&M, start and shutdown costs, emissions costs and ramp costs.

name: SRMC
description: Highest short-run marginal cost of running generators

name: Min Capacity Reserve Margin
description: Minimum capacity reserve margin for capacity planning

name: Planning Peak Load
description: Peak load in the current capacity optimization period (e.g. year)

name: Capacity Price
description: Average price paid for capacity in the region

name: Total Cost
description: Total of fixed and variable generation costs

name: Peak Load
description: Peak load across the current period

name: Min Capacity Reserve Margin
description: Minimum capacity reserve margin for capacity planning
